  "action_required": true,

  "body": "Director ratified two follow-on directions after seeing the Thingalog chart land cleanly: (1) establish master/replicant discipline so openbraid knows when it is authoritative for an orgdef artifact vs mirroring an authoritative copy elsewhere (e.g. github); (2) surface more of the orgdef content (org-level vision/values/policies + per-position responsibilities/deliverables/job-charter) so openbraid can become the canonical WYSIWYG editor. Director will work with you directly on editor mechanics; this memo captures the data model + display surface in particular detail on fields to surface. Full content in companion .body.md.",
  "body_ref": "2026-05-11-1730--orgdef-strategist--openbraid-engineer--master-replicant-and-fields-to-surface.body.md",

